description: It prevents complete darkness during Mains Supply failure. Light is almost half in Inverter Mode operation during Mains failure.

title: Syska SSK-TL-8605l (10 watts table lamp)
description: This is a better product than all other table lamps from syska brand😀, as its illumination is 10 watts which is good illumination and with this it's color tremperairure is 4300k-4700k which works as EYE protection👁. Along with this product comes with 1YEAR ☑️warrenty, but there is come drawback in this product that it is written that is will run for 3 hours on full light mode but it slow down completely after burning only half an hour on full charge and its does not have an over charging indicator, meaning it will not be know when it is fully charged☹️.if all this system was given than  this product would have been the TOP👍 product of the syska brand.....
